summary:
- Education professional in English communication skills
- Over 15 years of experience in the field of education
- Research Master Communication & Information Sciences (Tilburg University)
- Former secretary board of examiners
- Specific contexts: 
  * English in the (inter)national military context
  * English in the (inter)national Attractions and Theme Parks industry
  * English in the (inter)national Leisure & Events industry
  * (socio-)Linguistics, language teaching theory, language teaching didactics, curriculum development & testing for language learning
- 10 years experience as online content creator (hobby: blog/ Youtube)
